'''September 27''' is the 27th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  and its day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Wadō|ja|文和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1352|ja|1352|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Northern Court ({{ill|Kitachō|ja|北朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) changed its era name from {{ill|Kangō|ja|Kan'ō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1860|ja|1860|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – A 77-member mission to America ({{ill|Emissary to America|ja|遣米使節団|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) returned home after signing the [[Treaty of Amity and Commerce (United States–Japan)|Japan–US Treaty of Amity and Commerce]].

== Births ==
