== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1352|ja|1352|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – The Northern Court ({{ill|Kitachō|ja|北朝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) changed its era name from {{ill|Kangō|ja|Kan'ō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} to {{ill|Bunwa|ja|文和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1860|ja|1860|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – A 77-member mission to America ({{ill|Emissary to America|ja|遣米使節団|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) returned home after signing the [[Treaty of Amity and Commerce (United States–Japan)|Japan–US Treaty of Amity and Commerce]].
== Births == * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1829|ja|1829|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 24|ja|10月24日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Takeichi Mizusan|ja|武市瑞山|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Hanpeita), a pro-sonnō activist and swordsman († {{ill|1865|ja|1865|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Yōchō|ja|弘化|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1848|ja|1848|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Nakagawa Gorōji|ja|中川五郎治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , considered the founder of variolation († {{ill|1768|ja|1768|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
